sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Auth
    participant DB

    Client->>+API: POST /api/login
    API->>+Auth: Validate credentials
    Auth->>+DB: Query user
    DB-->>-Auth: User data
    Auth-->>-API: Token
    API-->>-Client: 200 OK + Token

    Client->>+API: GET /api/data (with token)
    API->>Auth: Verify token
    Auth-->>API: Valid
    API->>+DB: Fetch data
    DB-->>-API: Results
    API-->>-Client: 200 OK + Data
